bar (c) Henrik Theiling
=======================

Project home page at:
   http://www.theiling.de/projects/bar.html

Main source code distribution site:
   http://www.theiling.de/downloads/?name=bar

Getting Started
---------------

Please invoke

   $ ./bar -h

for help.

For using this, you can copy the shell function 'bar_cat' to your
own install scripts.  To extract the function body, use:

   $ ./bar -D > bar_cat.sh

Enjoy! :-)
